<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Bibliographie">Bibliographie</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Desmond_Tutu&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=24" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" title="Modifier la section : Bibliographie">modifier</a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Desmond_Tutu&amp;action=edit&amp;section=24" title="Modifier la section : Bibliographie">modifier le code</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<ul><li><span class="ouvrage" id="Battle2000."><span class="ouvrage" id="M._Battle2000."><abbr class="abbr indicateur-langue" title="Langue : anglais">(en)</abbr> M. Battle, <span lang="en">«&#160;<cite style="font-style:normal;">A theology of community: The Ubuntu theology of Desmond TuTu</cite>&#160;»</span>, <i><span class="lang-en" lang="en">Interpretation</span></i>,&#8206; 2000.<span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=A+theology+of+community%3A+The+Ubuntu+theology+of+Desmond+TuTu&amp;rft.jtitle=Interpretation&amp;rft.aulast=Battle&amp;rft.aufirst=M.&amp;rft.date=2000&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Ffr.wikipedia.org%3ADesmond+Tutu"></span></span></span> (Une théologie de la communauté&#160;: La théologie ubuntu de Desmond Tutu)</li></ul>
